{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quirkbound is an <strong>absurd</strong> and <strong>lighthearted turn-based JRPG</strong> with colorful 2D pixel art, bizarre yet charming enemies, a bangin\u2019 soundtrack, and award-winning* writing that\u2019s sure to warm your heart in a medically non-threatening way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*No awards have actually been awarded. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/explore_banner_frame.gif?t=1731245171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow the three young heroes Isaac, Clara and Naoto as they journey across the land to recover the Staff of Ultimate Power from the heinous <strong>Varakh</strong> and prevent <strong>the end of the world</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong> and <strong>fight</strong> your way through the otherworldly and box-filled <strong>Basement Dimension</strong>\u00a0and the luscious and overgrown <strong>Garden Forest</strong>!<strong>\u00a0</strong>Meet and<strong> talk</strong>\u00a0to whimsical characters and discover hidden stories!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/battle_gif_ratio_frame.gif?t=1731245171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in strategic turn-based battles against a cast of charming and deadly enemies! <strong>Block, dodge,</strong> and <strong>parry</strong> enemy attacks in real time with our even more award-winning** battle minigame!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/minigame_gif_2.gif?t=1731245171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slash, cast, shield, inspect,</strong> and <strong>stick</strong> your way to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>**Still no awards. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/collect_gif_frame.gif?t=1731245171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect powerful <strong>stickers, equipment,</strong> and <strong>spells</strong> to upgrade the party and temporarily satiate your <i>unending hunger for content</i>!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731245171","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731245171","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731245171","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731245171","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3022590,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Quirkbound is an <strong>absurd</strong> and <strong>lighthearted turn-based JRPG</strong> with colorful 2D pixel art, bizarre yet charming enemies, a bangin\u2019 soundtrack, and award-winning* writing that\u2019s sure to warm your heart in a medically non-threatening way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>*No awards have actually been awarded. Yet.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2711300/extras/explore_banner_frame.gif?t=1731245171\" /></p><p class=\"b